Dutch company Philips. Information, whether it's music or computer
files, is stored on a CD, a plastic disc, as a series of digital
pulses that is read electronically. The first music _ or ``album''
_ sold on a CD was ``52nd Street'' by Billy Joel.
</P>
<P>
   Q: I fairly often hear people use the expression ``gone south,''
