</P>
<P>
   Reformulated gasoline is an even cleaner burning _ and
considerably more expensive: perhaps 20 cents or more a gallon _
gasoline that reduces various exhaust emissions, including benzine,
a mixture of hydrocarbons. It already is sold in California.
</P>
<P>
   Q: Why is the Social Security cost-of-living increase so small
this year? Is Social Security running out of money?
</P>
<P>
   A: The 1.3 percent cost-of-living increase for 1999 is the
smallest since 1986, when it also was 1.3 percent _ but it has
