<P>
   OVER THE DECADES, A CONCENTRATION OF INCOME
</P>
<P>
   While all income groups earn more than they did 30 years ago,
most of the increase has gone to the top one-fifth of earners. That
group has increased its share of national income compared to 1967,
while every other group fell.
</P>
