<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-06 11:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0963 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CPT-EDLIFE-ONLINE-NYT     01-06 2108
