   WONG-COLUMN (Oakland, Calif.) _ The city of Oakland's first day
with Jerry Brown as mayor began in stereotypical Jerry Brown
fashion _ with a meditation at his industrial-sized live-work space
near Jack London Square. Stylistically, a meditation is pure Jerry
Brown. By WILLIAM WONG.
