<HEADLINE>
TEST YOUR LITERARY KNOWLEDGE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   One hundred years ago was a bountiful time in American letters.
Here are a dozen literary titles published in 1899, to be matched
with their authors. You pass with seven correct answers (a simple
majority) and earn an A with nine right. Answers are below.
</P>
