   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MARKET-SURGE (New York) _ Stocks surge more than 200 points to a
record, topping the 9,500 mark for the first time; merger activity
in the computer and telecommunications industries spurs a buying
frenzy. By Peter G. Gosselin. 1100 words.
</P>
