<P>
   BASKETBALL
</P>
<P>
   NBA
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA-DEAL _ The NBA and the players' union reached an
agreement after an all-night bargaining session to save what's left
of the season. The deal was struck between commissioner David Stern
and union head Billy Hunter. The agreement came just hours before a
key players' meeting and one day before the NBA's threatened
deadline for a settlement. (Denberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA _ League ends lockout. Season to begin early Feb.
(D'Angelo, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   w/BKN-NBA-ANALYSIS _ Analysis/comments from labor experts on the
lockout and deal. Was it worth it? (Joyner, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA-TV _ TV plans for the shortened NBA season. (Rogers
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA-Q&AMP;A _ Q&AMP;A on: winner/loser, revised schedule, playoffs,
training camp, signing of players, which teams have advantage, tv
plans, etc. (Denberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
