   FBN-FALCONS-SECONDARY _ Subtle changes in the Atlanta secondary
after the early season loss to the 49ers actually turned the
Falcons into a champion. The secondary, so bad at the first of the
year, got better. (Winkeljohn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
13-15.
