<P>
   FBN-NINERS-NOTES _ Notebook from San Francisco 49ers camp.
(Bunn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   FBN-FALCONS-CHANDLER _ Once considered an NFL malcontent, Chris
Chandler had heard about the problems in the Denver relationship
between quarterback John Elway and head coach Dan Reeves. So he was
a bit skeptical when the Falcons came calling two years ago. But
Reeves and Chandler bonded from the beginning _ both learning from
earlier mistakes _ and both have found in Atlanta a place to sink
roots. (Schultz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25-30. WITH PHOTO.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-DOLPHINS _ Dolphins offense went to the air in victory over
Broncos three weeks ago. That strategy won't work this time in
Denver. (Woods, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
