   COLLEGE FOOTBALL
</P>
<P>
   FBC-ROUNDUP _ College football news roundup. Georgia Tech hires
David Sollazzo of The Citadel as defensive line coach; Georgia
loses secondary coach Mickey Matthews, who will be defensive
coordinator at Baylor (Rogers/Towers, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
