<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Jan. 7 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Eddie Ibardolasa at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
BKN-NBA (Los Angeles) _ The NBA and the players' union reached an
agreement in principle today to end the 191-day-old lockout and
save what's left of the season. A season of about 50 games will
begin the first week of February. 
By Howard Beck. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
