<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-06 20:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1969 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CLINTON-SURPLUS-HNS &LR;      01-06 0514
