five-minute, award-winning parody of American advertising excess
called ``New Testament.'' Digital technology is changing the way
small filmmakers can now have a major impact on the industry using
personal computers with off-the-shelf software. (Marissa Roth/New
York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT2) PALO ALTO, Calif. -- Jan. 6, 1999 -- CIR-RARE-BOOKS, 1-6
-- Martha Blegen prepares to photogrpah pages from a work by
