<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-06 22:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2088 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKN-NBASETTLEMENT-HNS     01-06 1072
